translations: n．教区牧师（复数）：教区的主持牧师，负责管理教区事务。
· The rectors of the local churches gathered for a meeting.
当地教堂的教区牧师们聚集在一起开会。

sentences.sentence: They pledged to challenge the rectors in court.
sentences.translation: 他们誓言和校长到法院对簿公堂。

sentences.sentence: From 1982 until 1990, he was General Secretary of the West German Rectors' Conference in Bonn. Since 1990, he has been General Secretary of the German Academic Exchange Service.
sentences.translation: 从1982 至1990年就任设于波恩的校长联合会秘书长，1990至今任德意志学术交流中心秘书长。
